article.description: — Alex Barcello posted 17 points as BYU beat San Diego State 66-60 on Friday night.
article.headline: Barcello scores 17 to lead BYU over San Diego St. 66-60
article.linkText: Barcello scores 17 to lead BYU over San Diego St. 66-60
article.story: PROVO, Utah -- — Alex Barcello posted 17 points as BYU beat San Diego State 66-60 on Friday night. Te'Jon Lucas had 13 points for BYU (2-0). Nathan Mensah had 18 points for the Aztecs (1-1). Trey Pulliam added 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25------ Information from: Automated Insights, http://automatedinsights.com/ ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
